<subSubSection pageId="0" pageNumber="210" type="diagnosis">
<paragraph blockId="0.[1241,2123,693,884]" pageId="0" pageNumber="210">• Highly specialized fossorial marsupials, lacking eyes and external ears and with thickened snout shields; forelimbs with massive, spade-like Class; tails short, broad, and naked, terminating in knob-like structures.</paragraph>
